summary: Hi, I follow you for Killing Eve content, but where do the gif sets from episodes that haven't been streamed yet come from?...
question: Hi, I follow you for Killing Eve content, but where do the gif sets from episodes that haven't been streamed yet come from? According to schedule s2 epi2 comes out sunday evening, which it isn't yet in the US but you are already reblogging scenes from it? Am just wondering, thx for always keeping me up to date on everything Killing Eve ^^
answer: Hello, yes the episodes drop two days earlier in some countries legally and there’s ways you can watch ahead of Sunday when it airs in the US. I’m very impatient so I watch on Fridays on an Australian site (iview abc) by using a VPN (I use hoxx but others use hola) but I tag spoilers for people that would prefer to wait until Sunday. :)
